Code refactoring
----------------

- Install buildfarm modules into python' sitearch and make them importable
- Use configuration file instead of config.py which is imported
- Move standalone scripts under scripts/
- Use pisi methods if available to avoid redundancy
- Integrate repomanager into buildfarm executable
- Grab Pardus version from /etc/pardus-release to be more flexible

Features
--------

- Fork off a dependency checker after each run and send a report to the according
mailing lists and maintainers about the missing dependencies of packages

- Support for the removal of obsoleted packages

- A Web status page for current status

- Twit status updates ;)
